 The Regional Comprehensive Economic Partnership (RCEP) is to facilitate trade and investment, and provide a boost to economic recovery, Hiroaki Ito, general Manager of Yokogawa Sichuan Instrument Co., Ltd., said in a recent interview with Xinhua. The Regional Comprehensive Economic Partnership (RCEP) agreement will take effect on Jan. 1, 2022, according to the Chinese Ministry of Commerce.  Produced by Xinhua Global Service